high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the right to face the black shelf in the corner.
Pick the potato up from off of the black shelf.
Turn around, turn to the left and walk towards the stove top with the microwave on top.
Open the microwave, place the potato in the microwave, turn on the microwave, wait a second, open the microwave, take out the potato, and shut the microwave.
Turn around, go straight and turn right to face the black shelf.
Place the potato on to the black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the microwaved potato on top of the black shelf in the corner.

high_descs: Turn around to your left and walk across the room then face the black table to your right
Pick up the potato on the black table
Turn around to your right and head towards the microwave
Open the microwave, put the potato inside, let it cook then open the microwave again and get the potato
Turn around to your left, walk across the room and face the black table
Put the potato on the black table beside the container
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go across to the room, turn right to go to the small black table.
Pick up the small round and dark object from the black table.
Take the object and turn left, then right to find the stove.
Place the object in the microwave, turn it on, and then take the object out.
Turn around to go across the room, then right to the black table.
Place the object on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Cook an item in the microwave.
